[
  {
    "author_id": "1633948271049586432",
    "created_at": "2026-03-15T13:47:00+00:00",
    "id": "1869384720158493184",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": "12",
    "quote_count": "3",
    "reply_count": "2",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "",
    "retweet_count": "1",
    "text": "Course conditions are dialed in this week \u2014 the front nine came through spring aeration ahead of schedule and the greens are rolling pure. Book an early slot while the morning light lasts. #golf #ScottsdaleNational"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "1622039485710283520",
    "created_at": "2026-03-13T14:22:11+00:00",
    "id": "1867192048375920640",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": "21",
    "quote_count": "1",
    "reply_count": "4",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "",
    "retweet_count": "3",
    "text": "Our B-17 Flying Fortress exhibit is open. Stop by the bombardier station to see how a crew of ten worked and survived together across Europe. Docents on the floor all weekend to walk you through it. #aviationhistory #WWII"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "1583047192038475520",
    "created_at": "2026-03-10T17:08:33+00:00",
    "id": "1864837561029384704",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": "42",
    "quote_count": "0",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "",
    "retweet_count": "3",
    "text": "Trip planning tip: the Pa'rus Trail is flat, paved, and follows the Virgin River \u2014 the easiest way to take in the canyon at first light. The winter shuttle is on a reduced schedule, so check times before you arrive. #ZionNationalPark #nationalparks"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "1601938472058291104",
    "created_at": "2026-03-08T10:55:44+00:00",
    "id": "1862910384756192768",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": "45",
    "quote_count": "1",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "",
    "retweet_count": "2",
    "text": "Tempo over speed: the players dropping strokes this winter aren't swinging harder, they're walking off the rush. A consistent pre-shot routine is the most underrated club in the bag. #golf #instruction"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "1519384720194857600",
    "created_at": "2026-03-04T21:30:10+00:00",
    "id": "1859483720194857984",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": "33",
    "quote_count": "0",
    "reply_count": "1",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "",
    "retweet_count": "0",
    "text": "Tonight on Arizona PBS: a new documentary on the Sonoran Desert's night sky and the work to keep it dark. Check your local listings. #ArizonaPBS #publicmedia"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "1402938571028374016",
    "created_at": "2026-02-28T16:14:22+00:00",
    "id": "1856283910472058368",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": "18",
    "quote_count": "0",
    "reply_count": "2",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "",
    "retweet_count": "1",
    "text": "On this day in 1962, John Glenn orbited the Earth three times aboard Friendship 7. The capsule is on display in our Milestones of Flight gallery. #aviationhistory #spaceflight"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "1377482910583726081",
    "created_at": "2026-02-21T09:02:55+00:00",
    "id": "1851039482710384640",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": "27",
    "quote_count": "2",
    "reply_count": "3",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "",
    "retweet_count": "4",
    "text": "Bryce Canyon in winter: hoodoos dusted in snow and far smaller crowds. Pack microspikes for the icy rim trails and check road status before you go. #BryceCanyon #nationalparks"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "1593847201948372993",
    "created_at": "2026-02-14T12:45:00+00:00",
    "id": "1847938201048573952",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": "39",
    "quote_count": "1",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "",
    "retweet_count": "2",
    "text": "The Waste Management Phoenix Open is in the books \u2014 another wild week at the 16th. Full leaderboard and highlights at the link. #golf #PGATOUR"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "1601938472058291104",
    "created_at": "2026-02-06T19:30:00+00:00",
    "id": "1843829105738264576",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": "55",
    "quote_count": "0",
    "reply_count": "5",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "",
    "retweet_count": "6",
    "text": "Walking the course instead of riding burns calories, keeps your rhythm steady, and gives you time to read the next shot. The data backs up what the old-timers always said. #golf #fitness"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "1622039485710283520",
    "created_at": "2026-01-25T08:10:33+00:00",
    "id": "1837482910583726080",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": "14",
    "quote_count": "0",
    "reply_count": "1",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "",
    "retweet_count": "0",
    "text": "The B-25 cockpit display has a fresh interpretive placard this week, with new detail on the Doolittle Raid. Come climb in and see the office those crews flew from. #aviationhistory #museum"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "1377482910583726081",
    "created_at": "2026-01-18T15:55:00+00:00",
    "id": "1833948271049586688",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": "22",
    "quote_count": "0",
    "reply_count": "2",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "",
    "retweet_count": "3",
    "text": "White Sands at sunset is one of the most photogenic landscapes in the system. Boardwalk loops are open and the dunes glow gold at golden hour. Pack water even in cool months. #WhiteSands #nationalparks"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "1633948271049586432",
    "created_at": "2026-01-11T07:48:19+00:00",
    "id": "1830192847561028608",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": "17",
    "quote_count": "0",
    "reply_count": "1",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "",
    "retweet_count": "1",
    "text": "Frost-delay reminder: when temps dip near freezing we hold tee times until the greens thaw to protect the turf. Call the pro shop before your morning round this week. #golf #Scottsdale"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "1622039485710283520",
    "created_at": "2026-01-04T18:33:05+00:00",
    "id": "1826483920184756224",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": "29",
    "quote_count": "1",
    "reply_count": "2",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "",
    "retweet_count": "2",
    "text": "School-group season is underway. Our flight simulator exhibit is booked solid with curious young aviators this month. Teachers, the spring tour calendar is open now. #aviationhistory #museum"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "1488203749182736544",
    "created_at": "2025-12-27T16:09:42+00:00",
    "id": "1820938472058291200",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": "48",
    "quote_count": "2",
    "reply_count": "6",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "",
    "retweet_count": "4",
    "text": "The DC-3 first flew in December 1935 and went on to change air travel forever. Rugged, reliable, and still flying nearly ninety years later. A genuine landmark of aviation design. #aviationhistory #avgeek"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "1488203749182736544",
    "created_at": "2025-12-19T09:21:58+00:00",
    "id": "1816738291047382016",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": "23",
    "quote_count": "0",
    "reply_count": "1",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "",
    "retweet_count": "1",
    "text": "The Doolittle Raid, April 1942: sixteen B-25s launched from the deck of the USS Hornet with no way to land back aboard. The planning and the nerve behind it still astonish. #aviationhistory #WWII"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "1377482910583726081",
    "created_at": "2025-12-08T20:14:30+00:00",
    "id": "1810384756102938624",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": "31",
    "quote_count": "0",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "",
    "retweet_count": "2",
    "text": "Saguaro National Park in December: cool trails, blue skies, and the iconic cactus stands all to yourself. Just minutes from Tucson. Sunrise at the Valley View Overlook is worth the early alarm. #Saguaro #nationalparks"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "1593847201948372993",
    "created_at": "2025-11-29T13:02:11+00:00",
    "id": "1804827193048576000",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": "26",
    "quote_count": "1",
    "reply_count": "3",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "",
    "retweet_count": "2",
    "text": "The Hero World Challenge tees off this week with a stacked 20-player field. Live coverage all weekend. Who are you backing? #golf #PGATOUR"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "1519384720194857600",
    "created_at": "2025-11-15T08:40:27+00:00",
    "id": "1798372910482736128",
    "lang": "en",
    "like_count": "19",
    "quote_count": "0",
    "reply_count": "1",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "",
    "retweet_count": "1",
    "text": "This week on Arizona Horizon: a look at how the Valley is preparing for the busy winter visitor season. Weeknights on Arizona PBS. #ArizonaPBS #Arizona"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "1601938472058291104",
    "created_at": "2025-11-02T17:55:48+00:00",
    "id": "1791928374650192384",
