    "like_count": "37",
    "quote_count": "1",
    "reply_count": "2",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "",
    "retweet_count": "3",
    "text": "The fall schedule is heating up and the race for player status comes down to the wire. Catch all the drama from the final events right here. #golf #GolfChannel"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "1583047192038475520",
