    "reply_count": "1",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "",
    "retweet_count": "2",
    "text": "Fall in Zion means golden cottonwoods along the Virgin River and cooler hiking weather. The Riverside Walk is an easy, scenic introduction to the canyon. Always carry water. #ZionNationalPark #nationalparks"
  },
